                        <interp inst="t18380402-name-445" type="given" value="ELIZABETH"></interp>ELIZABETH ASHFORD</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the wife of John Ashford. I was present when the prisoner was married to Ann Mary Ashford, on the 1st of February, 1836, at St. John's, Hackney—she has since died.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
