                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined</hi>. When the prisoner married my sister she was single—she had formerly lived with me—she was a brush<lb></lb>maker—they lived together for ten weeks before she was confined and died.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner, in a written defence, stated that his first wife had deserted him, and cohabited with another person, and that she had consented to his marrying again.)</p>
